result.adr_address: 210 Shanghai St, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.name: Tin Ngan Bird's Nest Company

reviews.text: If you are looking for a unique and exotic Chinese food experience this is the spot.  They have anything from fish maw soup to birds nest soup. You will not find any of these items on a travel food show.  Most dishes served here have medicinal properties so they are usually expensive but they are not here.
Gorgeous food with reasonable price
沒說笑，超高性價比，鮑參翅肚，價錢可以接受，沒吃過的一定要來，你衹要吃過一定會回頭
嘩! 我們7人, 3男4女, 食咗$3000, 有魚翅2煲, 鮑魚, 海參, 山瑞, 秘魯馬卡花膠湯, 重有木瓜燕窩, 桃膠, 燉椰皇, 蓮子燕窩甜品, 每人$400, 你話抵唔抵, 重要係食物好味, 質量一流, 去試吓啦!
舊酒原來好飲過新酒咁多，花膠迷人，仲有得即食，甜品唔駛100，魚翅撈飯三佰幾有交易，口淡淡埋嚟食啦
